    q: "What Bertazzoni appliances do you repair in Los Angeles?",
    a: "All current Bertazzoni US categories. Gas and dual-fuel ranges across three collections — Master (entry luxury, MAST486 / MAST366 / MAST304 model families), Professional (mid-tier, PRO486 / PRO366 / PRO304), and Heritage (premium with retro styling, HER304 / HER366 / HER486). Wall ovens (single and double, 30-inch and 36-inch electric variants), cooktops (gas, induction, and dual-fuel modular configurations), dishwashers (DW series — fully integrated and panel-ready), refrigerator columns (REF series, 24-inch and 36-inch single-zone and dual-zone), and range hoods (matching range and wall-mount configurations). Within Bertazzoni's actual US lineup we service the full range; 2014-onward manufacture dates dominant in our service mix. Note: Bertazzoni does not make microwaves, washers, or dryers under the Bertazzoni brand — those categories aren't in the US lineup."
