    <p class="lead">Diagnostic is $89, applied toward the repair when you approve the work. Bertazzoni pricing sits in the mid-luxury repair tier — parts ship from Bertazzoni USA distribution (Italian origin through New Jersey warehouse), typical 7-14 day lead for less-common items; common wear parts for the dominant gas-range igniter / electrode / convection service items on the truck for same-day completion.</p>

